        {
            "id": 6320209,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 亞電(4939)股價殺至跌停，跌停價46.2元，成交32,255張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4939:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4939\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4939-TW</a>)23日12:23下跌5.1元，股價跌停報46.2元，委賣1,670,000張，成交32,255張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為覆蓋膜。軟性銅箔基層板。補強板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4939:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4939\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4939-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲27.3%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.29%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+168 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-474 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+642 張</li> <li>融資增減：-806 張</li> <li>融券增減：+676 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
